Bwalo la milandu ku Zimbabwe lalamula kufufuzanso mtolankhani wa NY Times .
Bwalo la milandu ku dziko la Zimbabwe linakana pempho lakutuluka lachiwiri mu mlandu wa mtolankhaniwa New York Times.Mtolankhani wozilempha yekha Jeffrey Moyo akuimbidwa mlandu wokana moonekera lamulo bungwe loona za anthu olowa ndi otula la ku Zimbabwe pamene akuganiziridwa kuti anathandizira atolankhani a kunja kwa dzikoli kulowa dziko la kummawakwa Africa li chaka chatha.
Kathleen Mpofu - m'modzi mwa oyimira mlandu wa Moyo - wati mtolankhaniyu akaonekera ku khothi kukayankha mlandu pa 28 April.
"Oweluza mlandu, a magistrate,anakana pempho lawo. Kunali kovuta kuwateteza abambo Moyo kamba odandaura anabweretsa umboni wokwanira" Ampofu anaauza VOAkuchokeraku Bulawayo podzera mauthenga a inteneti a WhatsApp
"Zikuonetsa kuti a magistrate anadalira umboni omwe odandaula anapeleka okhudzana ndi mapepala achilolezo abodza omwe mtolankhaniyu anali nawo komanso potengera kutanthauzira kwa umboniwu, anapeza kuti kunali koyenera kuteteza odandaulidwayu.
Oyimilira mlandu wa Moyo anakhulupilira kuti mlanduwu uthakutsekedwa, potsatira ndi pamene bwalo la milandu koyambilira kwa mwezi uno linamasura ogwira ntchito ku Media Commission ya ku Zimbabwe, Thabang Manhika, yemwe amaganizilidwa kuti anathandizira kupanga zilolezo za bodza kwa atolankhani awiri a Newyork Times omwe amakhala mu dziko la South Africa omwe analowa mu dziko la Zimbabwe ndipo anatumizidwa kwawo. Moyo ndi Manhika amayankha milandu yawo mosiyana.
Boma la Zimbabwe lati Moyo komanso Manhika onse anaphwanya lamulo la bungwe loona za anthu otuluka ndi olowa mdziko.
Mlembi wokhazikika wa unduna wa zofalitsa nkhani Ndabaningi Nick anaikirapo ndemanga pachigamulo cha la chiwiri.
"ife tikungofuna kuonetsetsa kuti pali lamulo ndi dongosolo. Ngati wina wapalamula mulandu kapena akukayikilidwa, adzakhala ndi tsiku lawo mu bwalo lamilandu ndipo zotstira zawo sizili mmanja mwathu,zili mmanja mwa dongosolo la chilungamo ndi milandu.
Tabani Moyo wogwira ntcito ku Media Institute of Southern Africa,kapena kuti MISA, waitanira kuti mtolankhaniyu achite naye mwa chilungamo
"MISA Zimbabwe yatsindika za kufunika kwa kuyesa oganizilidwa mlandu mwa chilungamo. Uwo ndiye udindo wathu njira yonse mpaka pothera mlanduwu. Chomwe tikunena ndichakutiiye, monga mzika ili onse, akuyenera kupatsidwa mwai wakuyesedwa mwa chilungamo,".
Moyo, mbadwa ya dziko la zimbabwe, izakakhala kundende kwa dzaka 10 ngati itapezeka yolakwa.
Apolisi a dziko la Zimbabwe aletsa misokhani ya chipani chotsutsa chachikulu.
A police ku Zimbabwe anatchinga chipani chotsutsa chachikulu m'dzikomo kupangitsa misokhano yokhudzana ndi zisakho zobwera pa 26 march pa mipando yomwe ilibe adindo chichitikileni chisankho chachikulu mu 2018. Apolisi ati akaniza ku mavhunga, komwe ndi pafupifupi 80 kilomitazi ku mmawa kwa Harare. akufuna kuonetsetsa kuti pali mtendere komanso bata.
Apolisi anakakhalira kumalo komweko usiku wa Lachisanu mu Marondera, komwe mtsogoleri wotsutsa wa Zimbabwe anali, gulu la Citizens Coalition for Change, Nelson Chamisa amayenera kuwayankhura anthu owatsatira Loweluka.
"Ndife chipani cha mtendere, chipani chokhala pa lamuro," anatero.
Chimisa wati chipani chake sichifuna zolimbana ndi anthu. Wati boma linakaniza chilolezo chopangitsira msonkhano ,ndipo chipani chinapempha chilolezo kuti abwere kuti azafotokoze za chimenechi, Iye anafotokozera omutsatira kuti sakufuna kuti ndale zakuzimbabwe zipangitse imfa ina iliyonse. Ndipo Iye anaonjezera kuti chomwe Boma silikudziwa ndichakuti kuti kuno ku mombera, kufika iye ndikokwanira.
Mukucheza nawo Lamulungu, Fadzayi Mahere yemwe ndi woyankhulira wachizimayi wa bungwe la Citizen Coliation for Change wati chipani chake sichinali chokondwa ndi kusachita bwino komwe bungwe loyendetsa zisankho laku Zimbabwe komanso achitetezo apolisi amakondera chipani cholamura cha ZANU-PF.
Msonkhano wathu unapitilira kukanizidwa pamene ZANU-PF galimoto yawo ya msonkhano ndikuchita zina zosaloledwa mudera lomwelo, "iye anatero. "olo kamodzi sanapepheko chilolezo olo kudziwitsa azachitetezo apolisi, pomwe kuphhwanya lamulo kumeneku amkchitira ife. kwa ife ndikuthandizira anthu abata amuderalo. Chomcho mazana omwe anatuluka kuti akamve mtsogoleri wadziko Chimisa akuyankhura panalibe kukaika kwina kulikonse kuti mbadwa za dziko zakomzeka kuchita chilichonse chomwe angachite pakubwezeletsanso ulemu wawo. tinapitilirabe kupempha.
okhwimitsa chitetezo a dziko la Zimbabwe akana kuikirapo ndemanga pa kuletsa Citizen Coliation for Change mu Marondera. Anapereka kalata kwa otsutsa kuti amkafuna nthawi kuti akomzekere kuti awonetsetse kuti kunali mtendere m'nthawi ya misokhano. Sabata ziwiri zapitazo kunali ziwawa zomwe zinatsogoleledwa ndi otsatira omwe akukaikilIdwa achipani cholamura cha ZANU-PF ku msonkhano wa Citizens for Coliation Change zadzetsa imfa za anthu awiri komanso kuvulara kwa anthu khumi ndi awiri.
Alexander Rusero yemwe ndi mphuzitsi wamkulu wa ndale wakale pa sukulu yaukachenjede ya Harare Polytechnic, wati okhwimitsa chitetezo komanso zipani zandale zikuyenera kuthetsa ziwawa pamisonkhano yaotsutsa
Okhwimitsa chitetezo amanga anthu 16 otsatira chipani cha ZANU-PF omwe akuganizilidwa ndikuzengedwa kuti anayambitsa ziwawa ndipo akuyankha mulandu wakupha molumikizana ndi imfa zomwe zachitika ku misonkhano ya otsutsa.
Nyengo yoyandikira zisankho kunadzadza ndi ziwawa zomwe anthu anamwalirapo komanso ambili anavulala kuchokera 2000 pamene chipani chotsutsa cha mphamvu chinauka
Bwalo la milandu ku Zimbabwe lachotsa kuimitsidwa kwa ntchito kwa miyezi itatukwa amphunzitsi omwe amanyanyala ntchito za boma.
Bwalo lalikulu la milandu la Zimbabwe lachotsa kuimitsidwa pa ntchito kwa miyezi itatu kwaaphunzitsi omwe amanyanyala ntchito ndi boma, kulamulira kuti unduna wa za maphunziro unadutsa malire a mphamvu zake. Aphunzitsiwa anapanga zionetsero posagwira ntchito sabata yathayi chifukwa cha kusakhutitsidwa ndi malipiro awo monga momwe ma sukulu akuyenera kutsegulilidwanso patatha kuima kwa nthawi yayitali chifukwa cha mlili wa COVID 19. Maphunziro a ana akumanizana ndi moto kuwiri.
Bwalo la milandu lalikulu ku Zimbabwe lagamula kuti kuimitsa ntchito aphunzitsi omwe amapanga zionetsero pa kusagwira ntchito yawo komwe a Evelyn Ndlovu, omwe ndi nduna ya maphunziro a pulayimale komanso sekondale anachita, ndikosavomerezeka pa malamulo.
A Noble Chinhanu ochokera kubungwe loona za ufulu wa anthu la, Zimbabwe Human Rights Forum anaimilira aphunzitsiwa ku bwalo la milandu
"Tinakwanitsa kupeleka mfundo zathu mu bwalo lamilandu ndipo oweruza milandu watipatsa lamulo lomwe lapangitsa uthenga womwe unapelekedwa ndi nduna ya zamaphunziro a pulayimale ndi sekondale unali wosavomerezekandi malamulo," anatero a Chinhanu. "Tinakwantsa kuonetsera kuti omwe timawaimilira pa mlanduwu ali ndi ufulu wakuti asayimitsidwe motero komwe kudali kuphwanyandondomeko za ogwira ntchito za boma mu dzikoli."
Ogwira nchito ku ma ofesi a boma sanaikirepo ndemanga pa chigamulo ca bwalo lamilanduchi
Masukulu ku Zimbabwe anatsekedwa chifukwa cha Mlili wa COVID 19 ndipo amayembekezerekakuti atsekulilidwe sabata yathayi.
A Gibson Nyikadzino, ochitilapo ndemanga pankhani za ndale oima paokha, ati boma ndi aphunzitsi athetse kuima kwa kuphunzitsaku mwa nsanga chifukwa ophunzira ndi omwe angapitilire kuvutika.
"Tikuona kuti pachuluka kukhumudwa komanso kulowetsapo ndale pa izi kuchokera kwa ogwirantchito," anatero Nyikadzino. "Alibe chidwi kuti amvetsere zomwe owalemba ntchito akunena. Pali ma gulu amene akukhudzika kamba ka izi, ndiye chimene chikuyenera kuchitika ndi kupita kukapanga zokambilana zokhudza magulu atatu ndi mtima wokuti agwilizane chinthu chimodzi."
Utatu womwe akukamba ndi boma,ogwira ntcito komanso pa kampani omwe si a boma.
A Sifiso Ndlovu ochokera ku bungwe la Zimbabwe Teachers Association lomwe ndi bungwe lalikulu pa mabugwe onse a mgwilizano wa aphunzitsi, wati akatswili pa maphunzirowa akufuna kubwerera ku ntchito koma akufuna ndalama zawo za malipiro zikwezedwe kuti azizisamalira okha.
"Pali ena omwe amakanika kuyenda: iwo omwe amachokera ku ma sukulu akutali. Iwo akuvutka chifukwa cha kusowa kwa zipangizozi," anatero Ndlovu. "Komanso pali ena omwe akuti akamakhala kufupi ndi kusukulu zawozo amavutika kupeza chakudya cha tsiku ndi tsiku. Izi ndizomwe zikumawakanikitsa kupezeka nthawi zonse.Tikukhulupira kuti tikalandira malipiro sabata la mawa la chiwiri zinthu zibwerera m'chimake. Komabe izi sizikutanthauza kuti aphunzitsiwa ndi okondwa ndi ndalama zowe amalandira. AKufunabe kuonjezeredwa malipiro."
Taungana Ndoro, ndi oyankhulira unduna wa maphunziro a pulaimale ndi sekondale ndipo wati zinthu mu masukulu tsopano zili molimbikitsa.
"Tayendera masukulu a boma komanso omwe si aboma, ndipo ndife okhutitsidwa ndi momwe kuphunzitsa komanso kuphunzira kukuchitikira," anatero Ndoro. "ndi zoona kuti pali ma sukulu ena patalipatali omwe akukumana ndizopinga pang'ono."
Nkhani ya malipiro ikuchokera mu October chaka cha 2018 pamene boma linasiya kulipira ogwira ntchito m'boma kudzera mu ndalama za kunja za U.S dollar kubwerera ku ndalama ya ku Zimbabwe ya Zimbawean dollar. Ndalama yatsopanoyi yakhala ikutsika mphamvu pang'ono ndi pang'ono, zomwe zinapangitsa kuti ndalama yomwe aphunzitsi amalandira itsike kufikira pa $100 pa mwezi. Aphunzitsiwa akufuna adzilandira $540 yomwe ankalandira mu chaka cha 2018
Sabata yatha aphunzitsiwa adakana ganizo la boma kui akweze ndi $20 pa $100 iliyonse mophatikizapo zolimbikitsira zina monga ngongole za nyumba
Boma laZimbabwe lalamula ogwira ntchito omwe analandira katemera kubwerera ku ntchito
Boma la Zimbabwe lalamura ogwira ntchito mboma omwe analandira katemera otetezaku mlili wa COVID 19 kuti abwerere kuntchito pompopompo patadutsa nthawi yopitilira chaka yomwe ogwira ntchitowa akhala akugwirira ntchito ku nyumba, poona kuchepa kwa chiwerengerocha anthu atsopano opezekandi kachilombokamu dzikoli.
Adindo alengezanso kuti aliyense wogwira ntchito m'boma amene alibe umboni woti anabayitsa katemerayu adzayimitsidwa kuti asapite ku malo ogwilira ntchito ndipo adzalandira chilango, kuphatikizapo kusalandira malipiro awo.
Mu mawu ake sabata ino, Presidenti Emmerson Mnangagwa ndi boma lake ati akufuna ogwira ntchito ake ayambe kupezeka. Lachiwiri lapitali,Motswatswa, nduna ya zamauthenga, anati chiwelengero cha anthu ogonekedwa ku chipatala kamba ka COVID 19 chikumka chikutsikira pang'ono ndi pang'ono
" Izi zikuonetsetsa kuti njira zothetsera mavuto za dziko zokhazikitsidwa ndi boma zikupindura. …Poona kutsika kopitilira kwa chiwerengero cha anthu atsoano opezeka ndi kachilomboka komanso omwalira, mophatikizana ndi kuchepa kwa kufulumira kwa kupezeka ndi kachilomboka zomwe zikuonetsa kuti kupatsirana mu derali kwatsika, malo onse olowera akuyenera kutsegulidwanso, koma kuonetsetsakuti njira zonse zoyenera kugwilitsidwa ntchito popewera mlili wa COVID 19 zizitsatilidwa," iye anatero
Choncho njira yakatemera okakamiza sinalandilidwe ndi ogwira ntchito m'boma onse.
Obert Masaraure Mtsogoleri wa Almagamated Rural Teachers of Zimbabwe, wati ogwira ntchito atengera nkhaniyi ku bwalo la milandu ngati boma likakamilebe.
Mgwirizano omwe unachitika ndiogwira ntchito M'boma mulibemo kukakamiza kubaitsa katemera.
Ndiye ngati ma ofesi antchito zaboma akufuna kulentsa ogeira ntchito m'boma omwe sanabayitse iwo akuphwanya mgwirizano wa pangano lawo ndiposizololedwa.
Chachiwiri, ogwira ntchito m'boma ali ndi ufulu ku ulemu wawo, ali ndi ufulu opanga zisankho.
Palibe aliyense angakakamizidwe kulowetsa zinthu zachilendo mmatupi awo, "anaounikira.
Dr. Norman Matara, wamkulu wa bungwe lamgwilizano wa ma dokotola la Zimbabwe Association of Doctors for Human Rights wati bungwe lake lazindikira kuti mayiko ambili akulunjika pa nkhani yakubaitsa katemera mokakamiza
"Ndichinthu chomwe tikutsutsana nacho kwambiri. Tikuganiza kuti kukakamiza katemera ndichinthu chomwe chikulimbikitsa kuchedwa kukalandira katemera.
Pali maganizo ambri azachiwembu omwe akuzungulira anthu akanena kuti akukakamizidwa kubaitsa katemera.
"Tikuyenera kumvera zonena za anthu,kufalitsa uthenga wa bwino wa katemera, momwe amagwilira ntchito kenakonso kulimbikitsa anthu kuti abayitse katemerayu osati kuwakakamiza kubaitsa katemerayu.," iye anatero.
Koma a Sifiso Ndlovu ochokera ku Zimbabwe Teachers Association avomerezana ndi maganizo a boma
"mwachidziwikire, ogwira ntchito onse akuyenera abayitse katemera.
izi akupanga osati kuti aziteteze okha koma kuti ateteze anzawo ogwira nawo ntchito
Umboni wa a sayansi ukuonetsa kuti ngati munthu anabayitsa katemera yense nthendayi ikumabwera ndi mphamvu yochepa
Tsono chosabayitsira ndi chiyani? Palibe cholakwika kapena tchimo popanga zimenezi," anatero
Anthu pafupifupi 3.3 miliyoni abayidwa kawiri katemerayu, pamene anthu pafupifupi 86,000 alandira wachitatu.
Mzika zambili za ku Zimbabwe zakana kubayidwa katemerayu ponena kuti sakumukhulupilira makamaka katemera wopangidwa ndi mzika zadziko la China wotchedwa Sinopharm ndi Sinovac.
Boma la Zimbabwe laimitsa pa ntchito aphunzitsi omwe amapanga zionetsero
A dindo ku Zimbabwe ayimitsa pa ntchito aphunzitsi omwe amapanga zionetsero kuti akhale miyezi itatu asakulandira malipiro pa kusamvana komwe kutapangitse masukulu ambili kuti akhalebe chitsekere. Aphunzitsiwa anapanga zionetsero pa kuima kugwira ntchito chifukwa cha kufuna kubwezeretsedwa kwa malipiro awo.
A Evelyn Ndlovu omwe ndi nduna ya za maphunziro a ku pulayimale ndi sekondale , madzulo a lachinayi anati kunyanyara kwa aphunzitsi kwaimitsidwa kutengera kuzengeleza kwawo koyambiranso kugwira ntchito posatengera kuti boma lawaonjezera malipiro awo omwe amalandira ndi 20 pa 100 aliyense.
"Onse ogwira ntchito ku undunawu omwe sanabwere kuntchito kuyambira kutsekulilidwa kwa ma sukulu pa 7 February, 2022 ayimitsidwa kwa miyezi itatu ndipo sadzilandira ndalama. Munthawi imeneyi aliyense sakuyenera kutchinga kapena kusokoneza kufufuza kapena umboni okhudzana kusachita bwinoku kukuganizilidwaku," anatelo Ndlovu. "Zoyenera kuchita zichitika mustutsana ndi aliyense yemwe sagwira ntchito zawo ndi maudindo awo."
Ma sukulu aku Zimbabwe amayenera kutsekulilidwanso sabata ino patatha nthawi yaitala chifukwa cha mlili wa COVID-19. K oma aphunzitsi anakana kuyambiranso ntchito, akupempha kuonjezeledwa malipiro. Pakali pano akulandira pafupifupi $100 pa mwezi.
Lachiwiri Boma laonjezera 20 pa 100 aliyense mu malipiro ndi zina zowalimbikitsa, monga maphunziro aulele kwa ana awo komanso ngongole za manyumba. Koma aphunzitsi akana zimenezi kuti ndizosakwanira.
Obert Masaraure, wapampando wa Almagamated Rural Teachers Union for Zimbabwe, anauza VOA kuti kuimitsa ophunzitsa kukupangitsa kupempha bwalo la milandu kwa changu kuti lillengeze kuti kuimitsidwa kwawo sikololedwa ndi lamulo.
"Malamuloa a kagwilidwe ntchito ka m'boma akufotolkozamomveka bwino momwe anthu angayimitsilidwe pa ntchito. Sitili mu dziko losakhazikika momwe aliyense amangodzuka ndikulengeza zinthu zosalumikizana komanso zosiyana ndi lamulo." anatero Masaraure. " Taona kuti a nduna azzichotatsa okha pa lamulo, choncho sangathe kuyankhura mololezedwa pa nkhani za maphunziro chifukwa achita mosagwirizana ndi lamulo lalikulu la dziko poimitsitsa mwachisawawa aphunzitsi a ku Zimbabwe. Tikuwaimitsa iwo pa ntchito pakuti achita mosemphana ndi lamulo."
Kusamvetsetsana pa nkhani a malipiliro kunayamba mbuyomu mu chaka cha 2018 pamene boma linasiya kulipira aphunzitsi mu ndalama ya ku nja ya Dollar(U.S dollar) kupita kupita ku ndalama ya ku zimbabwe ya dollar (dollar ya Zimbabwe). Ndalama yatsopanoyi yakhala ikutsika mphamvu pang'ono ndipang'ono zomwe zanapangitsa kuchepa kwa ndalama zawo zolandira pakutha pa nthawi.
Bungwe la aphuzitsi la zimbabwe la Zimbabwe Teachers Association - mgwilizano waukulu wa ophunzitsawa- llati akuyembekezera kukumana ndi akulu akulu a boma posachedwapa kuti akakambirane za kuimitsidwaku.
