Sukulu zambiri ku Zimbabwe zomwe zinatsekedwa kamba ka COVID-19 zinakali zotsekabe pomwe aphunzitsi akukana kubwelera kukaphunzitsa ponena kuti akufuna malipiro abwino.
Palibe oulutsa nkhani akupezeka pakali pano
Aphunzitsakulandira ndarama yosaposera $100 pamwezi. Boma laonjezera 20 peresenti pama lipiro awo komanso zolimbikitsa zina, Koma aphunzitsi akana kuti sizikukwanira
Pakalipano achinyamata ena akuphunzira paokha, ophunzira wina wazaka 16 wati," pempho langa ku boma ndikuti awonjezere malipiro a aphunzitsi kuti ayambilenso kugwira ntchito chifukwa sitikuphunzira. Zili ngati kuti tikulipira ndalama zophunzilira popanda chochitika, ndizopweteka pomwe makolo anga akuvutikira ndalamayo pomwe sindikuphunzira kalikonse.
Mkanganowu ukutitengeranso mmbuyo mu mwezi wa october 2018, Nthawi imene boma linasiya kuwalipira aphunzitsi mu ndalama zakunja U.S dollars, kusintha kubwera ku zimbawean dollars. Ndalama yatsopanoyi inatsika mphamvu.zomwe zinapangitsa kuchepetsa malipiro aphunzitsi
Obert Masaure wapamando wa Almagameted Rural Teachers Union of Zimbabwe, wati ophunzitsa akufuna kuti amlipiro awo akale abwelele ndipo kuonjezera kwawo ndi 20 peresenti ndipafupifipi kuti palibe chomwe apanga.
Tikupempa kubwezeletsedwa kwa malipiro, komwe kunachotsedwa ndi boma lomwe lilipo leroli, Masaraure aanati, uthengawu ndiomveka bwino kuboma. Tikufuna malipiro athu omwe timalandira mmbuyo mwa october 2018 omwe amakhara 540 U.S dollars. Tikudziwa kuti awa ofunthawa akuonjezera ma dollars ena ku malipiro athu- zimenezo sizikumveka
