Pamene ogwira ntchito a chisilikali nthawi zina amasamala zogulitsa za nkhondo za Russia, chuma cholowa "kuchepa kwambili kutengera ndi phindu lomwe amapezapo kuchokera ku miala ya mtengo yapatali yomwe amakumba komanso zachilengedwe," anatero Doxsee
