"Ngati dziko monga CAR litawalemba iwo ntchito yophunzitsa a silikali ena kuti awathandizire kumenya nkhondo, ndizofunikira kwa iwo kuti agwire ntchitoyo ndi kuimaliza bwino ngati akufuna kuti apitilize kupatsidwabe ncthito," anatero Doxsee
