Abusa a Rev. Athanasius Chidi Abanulo- Anagwiritsa nchito luso lawo lokhazikika mudzika lawo ku Africa kutumikira mwa machawi ku mudzi ya Alabama-Zikutengera kuti kodi ndinthawi yatali bwanji yomwe angafikire mabanja okhazikika omwe amabwera kuzapephera mu kachisi mwake Lamulung.
Mpindi zisanu ndi ziwiri ndipamalo pokoma makamaka kwa azungu komanso kwa iwo akhristu opuma omwe amapita ku mkumano wa mapemphero achiyankhuro cha chizungu ku Immaculate Conception Catholic Church mu mzinda waung'ono wa Wedowee." ukapitilira pamenepo, umasiya kumvetsera za anthu, anatero.
mMapephero amuchiyankhuro cha spanish pakatha ora limodzi, Wansembe wachi Nigeria mmodzi mwa otuikira ochuruka aku Afrika ku US- amadziwa kuti atha kutalikitsa nthawi yake yakuphinzitsa ndi kanayi. " mochuluka momwe ukulalikira, zabwino kwa iwo," anatero.
Pamene amachoka pa udindo waku america kupita pena, Abanulo anaphunzira kumanga utumiki wake mogwirizana ndichikalidwe chamudera lomwe akutumikira pamene akuthandiziranso mzimu wa dziko lake mapemphero achipulumutso.
Anthu aku Nigeria sakhala ndichidwi akabwera ku tchalitchi, Aanatero Abunulo. "Amakonda kuimba, amakonda kuvina. Mapemphero atha kutha maora awiri. Iwo sadandaura za zimenezo."
Pamene anali ndi zaka 18 ku U.S , Abunulo wakalapo pamaudindo oyang'anira zamapemphero komanso kugwira nchito za Ubusa mdziko monse. Ntchito zabwino zakhara zikupititlira kumveka ku matchalichi a chikatolika ku America. Mbadwadwa zobadwira ku amerika komko amuna komanso akazi analowa ku umsembe ndi usisitreri. Zigawo za U.S komanso mabugwe a katolika anasitha kukhala olemba athu dziko lonse polemba anthu omwe amafuna.
Zigawo za Birminham, komwe Abunulo amatsogolera mipingo iwiri, Wakulitsa kayang'ana malo okhazikitsa mpingo ndikuchulukitsa malo ogwilira ntchito achipepembedzo ngati Nigeria ndi Cameroon, anatero Abishop Steven Raica aku Birminham. Wamsembe ochokera ku Africa komanso wamphamvu ku chigawo cha Michigan komwe Raica amatumikira MMbuyomu
"Akhala akutithandiza kwambiri kuti tikwanitse kulinga mulingo komanso ukulu wa unduna omwe tili nawo kwa ife", anatero
Ku Africa ndi chigawo chimene tchaitchi cha chi katolika chakula mwachangu kwambiri. Kumene malo aansembe ndiodzadza, anatero Rev Thomas Gaunnt, Wankulu otsogolera Sukulu yaukachenjede ya Centre for Applied Research in the Apostolate, imene imapanga kafukufuku wa mpingo wa katolika.
Kutsika kwa ma nambala.
Ndizosiyana ndiku U.S kumene mpingo wa katolika wakumana ndimavuto pakulemba anthu omwe akulira mu mpingo mommo kutsalira kutsika kwa kabweledwe ka anthu ku mpingo kwa zaka teni zapitazi komanso kuonongeka kwa mbiri yomwe inafala ya nchititdwe ogonana wa pa mpingo.
Azimayi achikatolika komanso azibambo okwatira ndiokanizidwabe ku umsembe; Mtsutso ochotsa chiletsochi ukanathetsa vuto lakusowa kwa amsembe omwe sanapeze chikoka ndi chikhulupiliro kwa atsogoleri akulu akulu.
Zomwe tilinazo pano ndi nambala yochipa kwambiri kuyambira 1970 kulowa umsembe komanso usisiteri mudziko, Gaunt anatero. Iwo amene analowa mu zaka za mma 50 komanso 60 panopa ndi ndiokalamba, ndipo ma numbara akutengera kambiri ndianthu omwe akumwalira.
Kuchokera 1970 kufika 2020 ma numbera a amsembe ku U.S anatsika ndi 60%, kuengera mu kaundura yemwe anachokera ku GeorgetownCenter. Izi zasiya mipingo yopitilira 3,500 yopanda M'busa wamkuru okhazikika.
