Kukonza tsogolo la ntchito za mamangidwe za dziko la China mu Africapatatha zaka 10 zakubwereka
Dziko la China likuthandiza ndi chuma pa ntchito yomanga mopangira mphamvu yochokera ku moto wa miyala ku mmwera kwa Africa, posatengera chowinda chomwe anawinda mwezi wa September kuti athandizira mamangidwe kunja kwa dzikoli. Koma zomwe zomangidwa zomwe zikumangidwa ku South Africa ndi Zimbabwe ndi zochepa chabe koma zikuluzikulu zomwe Beijing yathandizira ku ma bwalo andege,njanji ndizomangidwa za mayiko ku Africa.
Mayiko ambili anali nako kukhumba kothandizira ntchitozi koma kukula kwa ngongole pa zaka zisanu zapitazi zomwe zikuchulikitsa chikayiko pokhudzana ndi omwe angathe kuti apange ntchto zina zomanga za ndalama zambili.
China ndiyodzipeleka kubwereka mayiko a mu Africa ndalama zokwana 153 billion pakati pa chaka cha 2000 ndi 2019 koma changu cha kubwereketsaku chitha kukhala chikuchedwerapo. Kudzipeleka kwa kubwereketsa ndalama kwa anthu a ku China kunatsika ndi 30 mu chaka cha 2019 oyelekezera ndi chaka chathachi, potengera ntchito ya kafukufuku ya Research Initiatve yomwe inapangidwa ku sukulu ya ukachenjede ya Johns Hopkins University School of advanced international studies. Kafukufukuyu amayang'ana kudzipeleka pa ngongole zomwe zimapelekedwa kwa obwereka pamene ntchitoyi ikuyambidwa
Mwachitsanzo ku Zambia, opeleka ndalama a ku China anapeleka 10.3 billion ku ngongole za mu zaka za pakati pa 2000 ndi 2010. Kuchokera mu 2000, Zambia yabwezako 1.2 billion kwa obwereketsa a ku China
Dziko la Uganda tsopano lili ndi ngongole ya China yokwana 200 million yokhudzana ndi ncthito yomanga bwalo la ndege , yomwe ikukuzamantha kuti dziko la China litha kulanda bwaloli. Mayiko onse anakana mphekeserayi kwa atolankhani a African mediapa nkhani ya kulanda kwa China bwaloli.
Kabwezedwe a ngongole kumbali ya Kenya kunalandira ngongole ya 4.5 billion kuti imange njanji yochokera ku Nairobi kufkira dooko la mu mzinda wa Mombasa ndipo dziko la China likuonetsa kuti iyang'ananso ndondomeko ndi mgwirizano patatha bungwe la African country's parliament kupeza kuti kusapindura ndi ngongole ku ma banki a China imavulaza opeleka msonkho.
Oyikira ndemanga enaachenjenjeza China kamba ka ndondomeko zobwereketsera zosaoneka bwinobwino zomwe zikutanthauza kuti China itha kulanda zomangidwazo pamene mayiko obwerekawa atalephera kukwanilitsa kubweza
Owira ntcito ku U.Skomanso ochokeraku Britain ati "misampha ya ngongole,"" pamene mayiko sangakwanitse kupeza ndalama zokwanira kubweza ngongole za dziko la China inaknzedwa kuti adzapeleke mwayi kwa Beijing kwaka nthawi. Mwezi watha, wamkulu wa Britains Secret Intelligent Service, Richard Moore, pocheza ndi BBC Radio 4 anati Beijing ithakupezapo ma dooko anangapo omwe ali ndi kuthekera kokhala podutsitsira zinthu pa sitima ndi zin zotero."
