Madando okhudzana ndi ngongole zopelekedwa ndi anthu a ku China
Dziko la China limalimbikitsa kubwereketsa ndalama ku mayiko a mu Africa pofuna zopindulitsa zambili pa zobzyala komanso mbili ya bwino pa dziko lonse lapansi yothandiza mayiko osauka., anatero Edward Miguel,mphunzitsi wa Environmental Resources Economics pa university ya Califonia ku Berkeley. Ikuyesera kufanana ndi U.S" ngati diko lopereka, anatero
Komabe, dziko la China limasiyana ndimayiko ena obwereketsa ndiwothandiza makamaka chifukwa chakusowa kauniuni komanso kuika poyera zinthu zomwe zimabweretsa mafunso ku Africa komansokumayiko aazungu, Miguel anakhulupilira choncho.
Kupatula ngongole zochokera kwa azungu, kapena mabungwe obwereketsa apadziko lonse lapansi monga World Bank , zomwe zimafunika ntchito komanso kuteteza za chilengedwe pa ntchito zopatsilidwa ndalama, chithandizo cha China ndi ngongole zopita ku Africa zinafotokozedwa ngati "zilibe cholowa kwa opeleka," zomwe zinakopa mayiko ambili.Koma mayiko a ku Africa makamaka omwe chuma chawo n'chovutika chifukwa cha COVID 19, amakumana ndi zovuta kubweza ngongole, anatero Hannah Ryder,Senior associate wa African Program at U.S think tank for strategic and international studies
" Dziko la China ndi mayiko ena akukhala ovuta kumvetsetsa mukupanga malonda opindulira onse," analemba Deborah Brautigamwa ku Shool of advance International studiesku John Hopkins University ndi Havard Business School mu zolemb limodzi.
Anthu okhala ku Dakar, Senegal, komwe bwalo la anthu 500 pa mkumano wa mgwirizano wa China ndi AFRICA (China-Africa cooperation meeting) unachitika mu November kuchokera pa 29 mpaka pa 30, akufuna zomangidwa zothandizidwa ndi ndalama zochokera kwa anthu a ku China koma popanda milingo ya ngongole ngati ya mma 1990, Ryder anazindikiraichi.
Obwereketsa ndalama aku China akuyembekezeredwa kubwereketsa ndalama zochepa kutsogolo kunokomanso osamalitsa polingalira kuti ndi tchito zanji ngongolezo zitathandizire, akatswiri atero. Ngongole zatsika kuchokera pamwamba mu 2014, Jili anatero
Kudzipeleka pa ngongole ndi zinthu zina zomwe zinapangidwa ku mkumano wa Africa-China Cooperation kunafika pa $40 billion, kutsika ndi gawo limodzi pa magawo atatu poyelekezera ndi $60 billion yomwe inapangidwa pa mkumano ngati omwewu mu chaka cha 2018.
Obwereketsa ndalama atha kuyeza ngongole pa kulosera za nthawi yamtsogolo mlili wa COVID 19 ukadzapita pamene mayiko a ku Africa adzakhale ndi ndalama zambili, anatero Yun Sun, otsogoleranawo wa East Asia Programku Stimson Center ku Washington. China ndichakuonetsetsetsa kusasiyanitsa pa anthu a ku China pa ntchito zamtsogolomonga kuombola ngongole zakale, iye anatero mu kucheza kwake ndi a VOA.
"ichi ndi chiopsezo pa ndalechifukwa ngakahale kusinthanaku sikofanana, zikuoneka ngati ndi kusinthana, ndipo kuti China ikupindulapo pa mavuto a Africa, choncho sindikuganiza kuti izi zichitika pompano ndipo chilungamo chake ndi chakuti kuumbanso kwa ngongole iyi kukutenganso nthawi," Sun anatero
China ikuyamba kulimba mtima mu nthawi yonseyi pakupanga maubale ndi mayiko a kunja ngakhale mayiko ambili a ku Africa akanai ndi nkhawa zokhudzana ndi vuto lakubwereza kwa ngongole mu zaka za ma 1980 ndi mma 1990 pamene mayiko anakanika kubweza ngongole, Yrdey akutero mu ndemanga yake mu African Business Commentary.Mabungwe a mayiko angapo anazichotsa izi zakuti mphepo ya ngongole zosakwanitsika zomwe zili ndi zifukwa kuphatikizapo kutsegura chuma chawo ku malonda ndi mayiko ena ,..............., komanso kutsitsa mitengo kwambili posinthana ndi ngongole," Peter Fabrics analemba mu Institute for Security Studies.
Kubwera mtsogolokufika pano, ndi ngongole zopelekedwa ndi dziko la China, mayiko a ku Africa nthawi zambili amathera kupempha, anatero Miguel, "Tinavomera kuti tidzatani" komanso "tili ndi ngongole yambili bwanji" ya China.
Dutch apeza odwara nthenda yatsopana ya Variant atamaliza kupeza anthu 61 opezeka ndi COVID mkatikati mwa anthu kwera magalimoto amatora.
Akulu akulu azaumoyo a Dutch Loweluka anena kuti apeza anthu 61 omwe apezeka ndi COVID 19 mkatikati mwa anthu omwe anayenda pa ndege Lachisanu kuchokera ku South Africa ndipo pakali pano akupitilizabe kuyezaku kuti aone ngati alipo wina wakhudzidwa ndi matenda atsopano a Ominicron Variant.
Opezeka ndimatendawa apezeka pakati pa anthu apaulendo pafup fupi 600omwe anafika pa bwalo landege la Schiphol pa ndige ziwiri zomwe zinafika Lachisanu boma la Dutch lisanaletse ndige zoyenda kuchoka ku mmwera kwa Africa chifukwa cha iwo okhudzidwa ndi Variant.
Akulu akulu azaumoyo a Dutch anati Loweluka anafuna kuti alumikizane ndi iwo apaulendo omwe anafika kuchokera ku South Africa, Botswana, Eswatini, Lesotho, Mozambique, Namibia, komanso Zimbabwe kuyambira Lolemba ndipo anawapempha kuti akayezetse mwachangu changu.
Apaulendo omwe anakwera ndege ya Lachisanu anasungidwa mosiyana ndi athu ena apaulendo omwe anapezeka ndi kachilomboka anasungidwa kwa okha ku malo ena ogona alendo oyandikana ndi bwalao la ndenge.
Wapampando wa undunawa zaumoyo wati kunali kusanadziwike kufikila Loweluka ngati oyenda paulendowa akhudzidwa ndi mthenda yatsopanoyi ya Variant.
Wapampando wa KLM, gawo la Dutch loona ndege zaku France , anati owona za ulendo wapa ndege iwo anayesetsa kufufuza kuti kodi ndondomeko zanji zomwe zinaikidwa Lachisanu mammawa poteteza anthu kuti asakhudzike ndi COVID 19 Pomwe akukwera ndege, omwe imanyamuka kuchoka ku Cape town komanso Johannesburg.
Malamulo patsamba la intaneti la kampani akuti anthu apaulendo akuyenera abweletse chitupa choonetsa kuti alibe matenda a COVID 19 chomwe ayezedwa mmaola 24asananyamukekoma sakuyenera kuonetsa chizindikiro chakatemera.
Zoopsa ndithu' Paula Zimmerman,wojambura zithunzi waku Dutch yemwe amabwelera kulendo okaona banja lake ku SouthAfrica Lachisanu mammawa, anati zithu pa anthu apalulendo mundegemo zinali zosokonekera, pomwe anasungidwa pa tala pamalo pokwelera kwa maola.
Zimmerman sanapezeke ndi matenda nthawi ya 4 koloko mammawa, pafupifupi maola 18 chifikileni pa Amsterdam, koma akuti anazindikira kuti anaima pafupi ndi muthu yemwe amadziwa kuti iyeyo wapezeka kuti ndiokhudziwa ndi matendawo.
