EU yaimitsa maulendo ochokeraku dziko la South Africa chifukwa cha maonekedwe a tsopano a COVID
Mayiko a mgwirizano wa mayiko a ku ulaya wotchedwa EU agwilizana kuti ayimitse maulendo ochokera kumwera kwa Africa chifukwa chakupezeka kwa maonekedwe atsopano a COVID 19, utsogoleri wa EU unanena lachisanu
Gulu la akadauro a zaumoyo kuchokera ku mayiko onse 27 omwe ali mu EU "anagwilizana zakufunikira kwakuika kuima kwadzidzidziku ndikukakamiza ziletso zakanthawi pa maulendo a ochokera ku mwera kwa Africa kupita ku EU.," mtsogoleri wa EU anatero pa tsamba la mchezo la pa intaneti la Twitter,. Malirewa agwira ntchito kwa mayiko a Botswana, Eswatini, Lesotho, Mozambique, Namibia, South Africa and Zimbabwe, oyankhulira bungwe la European Commission a Eric Mamer anatero pa tsamba la mchezo la Twitter.
Ogwira ntchito ku EU anatero kuti ulamuliro wa EU walimbikitsa kuletsa maulendo opita ku mayiko amenewa
Dziko lililonse mu mayiko 27 a mu EU ndilomasuka kutsata njira zatsopanozi pamene lakonda kutero. Ena ayamba kale kugwiritsa ntchito zilestozi
Anthu ogwira ntchito ku EU anena kuti palibe chiganizo chomwe chapangidwa pa mayiko ena muzigawo zina za dziko lapansi komwe kachilombo katsopanoka sikanaonekere, omwe ndi mayiko a Hong Kong, Israel, ndi Belgium dziko la mu EU
