Maonekedwe a tsopano a kachilombo ka Corona kamene kanapezedwa koyambilira ku dziko la South Africa kanabweretsa mantha pa dziko lonse lapansi pamene akafukufuku akuyang'ana kuti apeze ngati sikangagonje ku katemera.
Marc Van Ranst, kadaulo pankhani ya tizilombo amene anazindikira maonekedwe atsopanowa ku Belgium anauza Reuters kuti kunali kotheka kwambili kuti mzimayi yemwe anapezeka ndi kachilomboka anakatenga ku dziko la Belgium osati pa ulendo wa kunja kwa Europe.
