Nduna ya umoyo ku Italy a Roberto Speranza anavomereza lamulo loletsa kulowa kwa oyenda ochokera ku mayiko a South Africa, Lesotho, Botswana, Malawi, Zimbabwe, Mocambique, Namibia ndi Eswatini.
