Owona zanyengo ku zimbabwe akufana zithu zapamwamba kwambiri zokhudza kusintha kwa nyengo.
Azanyengo akuzimbabwe aonetsa kukwiya kwa Mtsogoleli wadziko Emmerson Mnangagwa pakuyankhura kwake pamkumano wa COP26, pomwe anapempha boma lake kulimbana ndi kaduludwe kamitengo kosasamala ndikusintha kwa nyengo. Owona zanyengo anati boma lilipakalikiliki opeleka malo kuma kampani, kwambiri ma china, kwa opanga mphamvu zamagetsi kuchokera kumiyara, zomwe a COPE 26 amafuna kuzithetsa.
Lachiwiri ku Scotland, Mtsogoleli Emmerso Mnangagwa anayankhura pa nsonkhano wa maiko wazakusintha kwa nyengo wa 2021,kudziwika ngati COP26, komwe anapepmpha maiko olemera kuti alipile chifukwa chowononga mpweya wamulengalenga pakuchotsa mpweya mulengalenga.
Anati maiko ovutika ngati Zimbabwe amalipira pazotsatirazi zakuonongeka kwa mpweyako.
Anapemphanso dziko lake kuti agwilizane polimbana nikusintha kwa nyengo.
Zimbabwe yaunikanso momwe dziko lawo lifunile kuthanizira, njira lodzipeleka ndi 40% pa malo aliwonse ochepetsera kuochotsedwa kwa mpweya mulengalenga kulunjika ku 2030. njira zapamwamba zakhazikitsidwa pakulunjika cholingachathu chachikulu pakusintha kwa nyengo ndikuzolowera komanso kukhazikitsa bata mu zigawo zathu zonse za zachuma, " anatero Mnangagwa.
Izi zimabwera panthawi yomwe owona zanyengo ku zimbabwe anapempha boma kuti Lerande chitupa chachilolezo chomwe chinapelekedwa posachedwapa ku kampani yama china kuti azikumba miyara yantengo wapatari kuti azigwilitsa ntchito pa mpamvu zamagetsi.
Bungwe la Center for Naturural Resource Governance nsi bungwe limodzi lomwe limatsutsana ndi chitupachi. Gululi limalimbikitsa mpamvu za chilengedwe, ndipo amaopa kuti kukumbidwa kwa miyarayi kudzapangitsa kuonongeka kwachilengedwe kwambiri.
Henry Nyapokoto wamkulu oyang'anira madongosolo a gululi, anati ndemanga ya Mnangagwa ikukamba zosiyana ndizomwe iyi waona zikuchitika.
Koma bomalakhala patsogolo kuyendetsa ndikulimbikitsa kukumba miyara paliponse pofuna kukwaniritsa chuma chakumiyara chokwana $12 billion. Koma kunena zoona izi sizingatheke Zimbabwe kupeza chuma chokwana $12 billion kudalira njiora zoipa zopangira katundu, kagwilitsidwe kolakwika,zimenezi zisiya chilema chachikulu ku zachilengedwe kape mbilri yakuonongeka kwa zachilengedwe. Tonse timadziwa kuti kukumba miyara yamtengo wapatali kumabwera ndikuononga kwa nkhalango yomwe imachotsa mpweya oipa komanso malo akhara zinyama zakutchire., " anatero Nyapokoto.
Nyapokoto anaonjezera kuti Zimbabwe imatulutsa mafuta komanso mpweya kuchipata chake chuku mpoto ndi Zambiya, Zochitika zina zomwe zikanapangitsa kuonongeka kwa chilengedwe.
Kupatura kukhudzika kwa mafuta komanso mpweya kwa kuonongeka kwa mpweya wa mulengalenga, pakhala voto loonekera pompano lolunjika mafutawa komanso kukumba mpweya kumamidzi kapena ku zachilengedwe. Malo alambulidwa chifukwa cha kukumba miyara komanso kumanga zinthu zina zomwe zithandizile kukumba miyara. Izo ndizosemphana ndikukonza zachuma zomwe iwo amakamba ku Glasgow'" Anatero Nyapotoko.
Anati Zimbabwe ili mu ndandanda wa maiko 10 akuononga chilengedwe. Ndi pafupifupi 300,000 ekara ya nkhalango zimaonongedwa pachaka.
Koma Byron Zamasiya wa bungwe la Zimbabwe Enviromental Law Association anati Mnangagwa ananena zoona mukulankhura kwaku ku COP26 zakulimbana ndikuononga chilengedwe komwe akupangitsa iwo ofuna Mphavu.
Ndiye nkhani yolimbana ndi kuononga chilengedwe ndyofunikira kumaikamo pamene pakuyankhulidwa za malo achilengedweochotsa mpweya oipa mulengalenga ku zimbabwe. Mitengo imagwira ntchito yoyamwa mpweya ndipoimayamwa mpweya owonongeka, omwe ndioyambitsa kwambiri kuonongeka kwa mpweya wamulengalenga. Chomwe tingafune ngati dziko ndikupeza njira ina yopezera mpamvu, makamaka kumamidzi komwe amadalira mkhuni ndipo zimaonjezre gawo lalikulu ku kuononga chilengedwe. tikuyeneranso kulimbikitsa maulimi ang'ono ang'ono omwe amasiyanda ndi ulumi akulu akulu omwe amafuna mindi yaukulu ndikulambula maro ankhalando akulu kuti pakhale minda, Anatero Zamasiya.
Bungwe la Enviromental Management Agency ku Zimbabwe lakhala likulipilitsa chindapusa anthu omwe amagwidwa akudura komanso kuyatsa nkhalango. Koma pakanali pano izi sizinaimitse kuduliwa kwa mitengo.
Zimbabwe yayamba katemera wa ana achisodera.
Boma la mtsongoleri Emmerson Mnangagwa lalengeza kuti likuyambakatemera wa ana achisodzera aku zimbabwe opyola zaka 16 polimbana ndi COVI19, yemwe watenga miyoyo pafupifupi 5,000 ndikukhudza anthu 13,000 mudziko, akatswiri owona zachipatara agwilizana nayo ndondomekoyi.
Wapampando ogwirizira zaumoyo komanso chisamaliro cha ana ku zimbabwe Amon Murwira anauza mtola nkhani Lolemba lapitali kuti pakadali pano dziko lakwani kupeleka katemera 38% pachikgawo cha anthu.
Ndipo iye analengeza zoyenelera ktuengera iwo opyora zaka 16.
Motengera ndi kaundunra wa azachipatara molingana ndi a Medecines Control Authority of Zimbabwe guide, katswiri owona zachipatara makamaka ku ana anavomeleza kulandira katemera kwa gulu lazaka 16 mpaka 17 ndi katemera wa sinovac COVID 19, " Anatero Murwira.
Dongosolo la gulu la ana azaka zachichepeleri linakaunikilidwabe. Unduna wafuna udziwitse anthu za katemera wa COVID19 yemwe akupelekedwa kwa gulu la anthu azaka 16 mpaka 17 anavomelezedwa. Boma la dziko Zimbabwe kudzera ku unduna wa zachipatala komanso chisamaliro cha ana ukuonetsetsa kuti Zimbabwe ikwaniritse kufikira aliyense ndikatemera pofika kumamaliziro a mwezi wa december 2021, " Iye anaonjezera.
Dr, Norman Marata mkulu wa Zimbabwe Association fro Doctor for Human Rights, ali ndichiyembekezo kuti dongosolori lichilutsa numbala ya anthu omwe abayitse katemera ndipo zithandizira kuti dziko lipite patsogolo kukwanitsa cholinga chopeleka katemera kwa aliyense.
Iyi ndi njira yabwino, koma tikukhulipilira kuti katemerayu apitilira kukhara waulele ndipo ana achisodzerawa sakakamizidwa kulandira katemera ku sukulu komanso ku sukulu zaukachenjede. Koma anthu apitilira kulandira katemera mwaufulu, " Iye anatero.
Itai Rusike, mkuli wa bungwe longothandiza la Community Working Group on Health in Zimbabwe, anayamikira boma polengeza zomwe zatahndiza dziko kufikira mulingo wake opeleka katemera kwa anthu akuzimbabwe mafupifupi 10 miliyoni kapena kuti 60% ya anthu pakutha kwa chaka.
Izi ndizofunikira pofuna kuteteza ana achisodzera ku kukhudzidwa ndi COVID 19 , kugonekedwa muchipatala ngakhale kuimfa, makamaka posapeleka mpata melili oopsa wa delta variant. Ndichinthu chofunikiranso kuti azaumoyo oyang'anira mma sukulu adzazidwa bwino ndimaphunziro ofunikira a katemera wa COVID 19 kuti atha kuthandizira kuphunzitsa ana asukulu, aphunzitsi ndi ena othandizira pa kufunikira kolandira katemera. ndizofunikilanso kuti atsogoleli amaderakuti khale akatstwiri otenga gawo lovutitsitsa pa COVID19 ndikukharanso oimilira kuti atha kulimbikitsa makolo ndi ana mmadera mwawo polandira katemera, " Anatero Rusike.
Zimbabwe yapeleka katemera yense kw anthu oposera 2.6 miliyoni kuchokera feburuary pomwe anayamba dongosolo yothana ndi mulili wa COVID-19.
Mtsogoleli wadziko la Zimbabwe akakhaka nawo pa msokhano wa COP26
Mtsogoleli w dziko la zimbabwe Emmeron Mnangagwa wati akapezeka ku COP26, akhala mtsogoleli oyamba wa zdiko la Zimbabwe kuyendera dziko la United Kingdom kuchokera nthawi yomwe Zimbabwe inatsutsa nkhani zophwanya ufulu wa anthu komanso kubela kwa zisankho, MNngagwa anatinso U.N rapporteur kuti boma lake linapanga zoyenera zokhudza mulandu wazisankho.
Pomalizitsa msonkhano wa pachaka wa chipani cholamula cha ZANU-PF Loweluka ku Bindura, mtonda otalika 80 kilomitazi kumpoto kwa zinda waukulu wa Zimbabwe, Mnangagwa anati akuyembekezeranso kudzakhala nawo pamsonkhano mu chaka cha 2021 United Climate Change Conference, omwe umadziwika kuti COP26, ku Scotland, omwe ukuyamba Lamulungu.
"Ndimfuna ndizdiwitse pamkumanowu kuti mawa mammawa(Lmulungu) ndikupita ku Glasgow, United Kingdom, patantha ndikudutsa zaka zoposera makumi awiri Utsogoleri wa Zimbabwe osapita ku United Kingdom. Ndaitanidwa ndi Nduna yaku Boris Johnson ndipo wauonetsa kuti titha kakumana maso ndi maso, chimodzi modzinso azitsogolieri ena ngati nduna yaku India andi enanso, tikukuman nawo, Anatero.
Mnangagw anatinso anali okondwa ndizomwe anayankhura a U.N. Special Rapporteur Alena Douhanatakayendera dziko la Zimbabwe kwa masabata awiri. Dziko la Belarus yapepha U.S ndi maiko ena azungu kuti achotse chilango chomwe anane kwa Zimbabwe pafupifipi dzaka makumi awiri zapitazo pakubera zisankho komanso kuphwanya maufulu a anthu.
Ife ngati boma, Ife ngati ZANU-PF, tinakutira ndi zomwe anapeza ndikutulutsa akatswiri a atolankhani a United Nations, tikuyenera kuziyamikira tokha. Sitinalakwitsepo, ndipo tizapitiliza kukhara ochita zolondolra. Iowo omwe apezeka akuphwanja lamulo akuyenera atule pansi maudindo awo, ' anatero Mnangagwa.
Koma mau otepedwa omwe anatulutsidwa ku nyumba youanganira mbadzwa zaku U.S ku Harare, Kazembe wa U.S ku United Nation Linda Thomas Greenfield anati chilango cha atsogoleri aku Zimbabwe sichimapweteka mbadwa zawamba.
Chilango chathu chikulundika pa munthu komanso mabungwe omwe anapalamula mulandu ophwanya ufulu wa anthu. Ndipo tikuyesetsa mbali ina iliyonse kuti chilango ichi chisakhudze anthu. Zomwe zikuchitika ku Zimbabwe ndizotsatira za mfundo zoipa zomwezinakhazikitsidwa ku zimbabwe.Zomwe zikuchitika ku Zimbabwe nsizotsatira zautsogoleri wawo. Sizotsatira zachilango chathu, ndipo tizapitiliza kukana kutsutsidwa kwina kulikonse kuti chilango chanthu chikuikidwa pa anthu mosayenera. Izi timatsutsidwa nazo ndi boma la Zimbabwe chifukwa amadziwa kuti vuto ndi iwowo pa zimenezi. Ndi zokhudza kuti mtolankhani wa paderedera anasankha kuyika izi mu uthenga wake womwe analemba," anatero Thoams Greenfield.
Bungwe la European Union anaika mokakamiza ziletso za mayendedwe ndi chuma pa mtsogoleri wa dziko la Zimbabwe wa nthawi imeneyo, a Robert Mugabe ndi ogwirizana nawo mu chaka cha 2002 potsatana ndi kubeledwa kwa zisankho komanso ma ufulu wa obadwa nawo. Mgwilizano wa mayikp pthedwa U.S onachita chimodzimodzi mu chaka cha 2003.
Kumayambiliro a sabata ino, mgwilizano wa mayiko wa U.S, Britain komanso bungwe la European Union mu mauthenga osiyana anati chumacha dziko la Zimbabwe chimavutika osati chifukwa cha ziletsozo koma chifukwa cha ziphuphu komanso kukanika kugwiritsa ntchito chuma cha dzikolo ndi boma.
Asilikali akale omwe anamenya nawo nkhondo ya Zimbabwean Liberation War amasulidwa atatha kupanga zionetsero pa kuchepa kwa ndalama za peshoni
Bwalo la milandu ku Zimbabwe la chisanu linalamula kumasulidwa kwa asilikali akale okwana pafupifupi 40 omwe anamenya nawo nkhondo yomenyera ufuluodziimira pa okha mu chaka cha 1970, patatha masiku anayi akuyesera kupeleka madando awo kwa mtosgoleriwa dzikolo Emmerson Mnangagwa pa nkhani yokhudzana ndi kuchepa kwa ndalama za peshoni.
Owayimilira pa mlandu pa mlanduwu ananeneza boma pa mlandu wapondereza ufulu wa mzika zadzikolo wa kuchita zionetsero, makamaka iwo omwe anatsutsana ndi lamulo la mtsogoleri wa dziko Mnangagwa.
Nkhalakale zpa nkhondozi anacheza panja pa bwalo la milandu la chisanu pamene oweruza otchedwa magistrate Babra Mateko analamula kumasulidwa atapeleka ndalama za chikole choyendera milandu cha $40. Iwo anamangidwa lolemba pamene amaeyesera kupita ku mao ogwilira ntchito a Mnangagwa kukafunsa ngati angakonze pa ndalama yosakwana $100 pa mwezi a peshoni
Paidamoyo Saurombe wochokera ku bungwe lo oimilira milandu la Zimbabwe Lawyers for Human Rights anayankhura ndI VOA atawapezetsa a nkhalakale pa nkhondowa kumasulidwa koyendera mlandu.
"Kupanga zionetsero ku Zimbabwe si mlandu, simlandu kupeleka madando. Makamakanso malamulo aakulu mdzikoamalora kutero," anatero Saurombe."Tsono pa chilichonse chomwe chingachitike zikuyenera kukhala mu malire oyikidwa ndi lamulo lalikululi(constitution) kapena zomwe zili zololedwa ndi lamuloli. Komanso omwe tikuwaimilira amatsatira zomwe lamulo la dziko limaloleza, choncho kunena kuti anapalamura mlandu zitha kukhala zosamveka.
Nkhalakalezi zikuyembekezeka kukaonekera ku bwalo la milandu kukayankha mlandu mwezi wa mawa. Malndu wa "kusokoneza mtendere ," womwe akuyankha aloi ndi mwayi opeleka choindapusa akapezeka olakwa pa mladuwu.
Powayankhura akuluakulu a chipani cholamura cha ZANU-PF lachisanu ku Bindura, pafupifupi ma kilomita 80 ku mpoto kwa Harare, Mtsogoleri wa dziko Mnangagwa anati nkhalakale za nkhondozi sanatsate dongososlo loyenera.
Bntchito zosiyanasiyana zakhazikitsidwa pofuna kupititsa patsogolo ulemu, chisamaliro komanso kuchita bwino pa chuma cha a nkhalakalewa pa mavuto aku masulidwa komanso podalira kwa ngwazizi," Mnangagwa anatero. "Koma ndikulimbikitsa nkhalakalezi kugwilitsa ndondomeko zoyenera mu chipanichi,osati panja pa chipanichi. Mfundo zawo zozama zithandizire kumangilira mfundo ya kukonda dziko lawo mu mitma ndi malingaliro awo ndikuwalemba mukuyesetsa kuti chipani cha ZANU-PF chipitilire kukhala chipani chosankhika chomwe chimatumikira anthu ake ndi mtima wonse
Ku bwalo la milandu,mmodzi mwa ankhalakalewa yemwe anazitchura Cde Tendai,anati iye mtima wake unatsika pansi atamva kuti amzake atulutsidwa pa belo chifukwa ena mwa iwo ali ndi matenda akabwerebwere
"Timakhudzika chifukwa cha thanzi lawo," anatero Tendai. "Tinali ndimantha kuti ena athakumwalira poti ankhalekale ambili ali ndi ziphinjo zambili. Tinadabwandi kumangidwa kwawo . Sitinapange ziwawa zilizonse, tiamalemekeza lamulo komanso boma lathu. Vuto lomwelinalipo ndi lakut: timafuna kusiya madando athu pakuti timalandira ndalama yochepa kutengera ndi momwe moyo wavutira."
Nkhondo yomenyerera kumasulidwa kwa Zimbabwe kuchoka ku ulamuliro wa azungu wa Ian Smith inatenga zaka 16, kuchokera chaka cha 1964 mpaka chaka cha 1980. Boma limapeleka ndalama za opuma pa ntchito kwa ankhalakale pa nkhondo okwanira pafupifupi 30,000.
Boma la Zimbabwe: Osabayitsa katemera wa Covid, osagwira ntchito, osalandira ndalama
Atsogolero a mgwirizano mokwiya ayankhapo pa zomwe boma la Zimbabwe linalengeza lamulungu kuti ogwira ntchito omwe sanabayitse katemera wa Covid 19 sadziloledwa kugwira ntchito ndipo sadzilipilidwa. Izi zikuonedwa ngati njira yopangitsa anthu ambili omwe akuzengereza kukabayitsa ku mmwera kwa Afrika kuti abayitse.
Ndabaningi Nick Mangwana amene ndi mlembi wa oulutsa nkhani, kumapeto kwasabataku anauza nyumba zoulutsa nkhani zoyendetsedwa ndi boma kuti onse ogwira htchito m'boma amene sanabayitse katenera wa COVID-19 sadziloledwa kugwira ntcito kuyambira lolemba.
"Palibe kuonjezera masiku kuli konse kuchoka pa 15 October pamene ogwira ntchito m'boma onse akuyembekezereka kukhala atabayitsa katemera wa COVID -19, kulephera kutero kwa osabaitsa sadzaloledwa kugwira ntchito. Kaphatikizira pamenepo kuti omwe sanabayitse ndipo sakugwira ntchitosadzalandira ndalama chifukwa nkhani ndi yakuti ngati sunagwire ntchito usalipilidwe," iye anatero.
Aphunzitsi a masukulu omwe ndi gawo lalikulu la ogwira ntchito m'boma ku Zimbabwe, ati tsiku lomaliza la lachisanu lomwe boma linanena anapanga a boma okha osakhudza iwo
Momwe zimakhalira, panalibepo mgwirizano okhudzana ndinkhani ya katemera," anatero Takavafira Zhou, mkulu wa bungwe la wa aphunzitsi la Progressive Teachers Union of Zimbabwe."Mfundo yathu ngati ogwira ntchito nthawi zonse timalimbikitsa anthu athu kuti akabayitse. Koma pasapezeke njira iliyonse yomwe chilimbikitso chomwe timapelekachi chitengedwe molakwika kuti chikhale lamulo kwa liyense kuti akabayitse katemera. Ganizo lathu ndi lomveka bwino: kubayitsa kukhale chisankho cha munthu osati lamulo. Tigwilire ncthito kufunikira kwa katemera-kufotokozera anthu athu momwe katemera amawathandizira iwo pokulitsa chitetezo cha mthupi mwawo koma zimenezi sizinachitidwe."
Boma la Zimbabwe lati labaya katenmera kwathunthu anthu okwanira 2,472,859 chiyambireni dongosololi linayambira mu February
Zhou anati anthu aku Zimbabwe amathawa kubayitsa katemera pa zifukwa zambili zomwe boma likuyenera kumvetsetsa kaye kuchokera ku zifukwa za zipembedzo zokhudzana ndi kusowekera chidziwitso pa nkhani za katemera wa COVID-19 kufikira pa kusowa chikhulupiliro cha pa katemera wopangidwa ndi anthu a ku China wotchedwa SINOVAC ndi SINOPHARM
Iye anati ogwira ntchito m'boma onse apitilize kupita ku ncthito pamene bungweli likuganizira zopita ku bwalo la milandu pa nkhani ya ganizo lofuna kuwachotsa ntchito
Anthuwa asiya kupita ku ntchito ngati pali kalata yowachotsa ntchito yochokera ku ma ofesi a boma a Public Service Commission. Komabe ingakhake kalatayi itapelekedwa, idzafunsidwabe pakuti lamulo lomwe likutsatidwa lidzayenera lioneke.Koma pakanali pano, aphunzitsi apitilira kupita ku malo awo antchito, obwezedwa mbuyo ndithu, ovutitika mu umphawi komanso zosautsa koabe akhalabe ogwilira ntchito boma," iye anatero.
Pakali pano athu omwe anadziwika kuti anapezeka ndi kachirombo ka Corona ku Zimbabwe alipo okwanira 132,333 komanso anthu omwalira ndi akchiromboka okwira 4,657 kutengera zotsatira zopezedwandi a Hopkins Coronavirus Resource Center, omwe amautsata mliliwu. Ogwira ncthito m'boma makamaka aphunzitsi anayambira kalekale kudandaura kukhudzana ndi kusoweka kwa zipangizo zokwanira zozitetezera mu kalasi pochepetsa kufalikira kwa COVID -19. Boma la Zimbabwe komabe likupitilizakunena kuti likupeleka ziangizo zokwanira polimbana ndi mliliwu.
Gulu losewera masewera acricket yakanika kupita kukaona ku Pakistan kamba ka chitetezo
Gulu losewera masewero a cricket la ku New Zealand lalengeza kutaya ulendo wokayendera Pakistan,potchura chfukwa cha mantha pa nkhani ya chitetezo la chisanu lapitali lomwe linali tsiku limene limayenera kukhala ndi masewero awo oyambilira, kutsatira kukura mulingo kwa chiopsezo kuboma la New zealand ndi Pakistan, komanso uphungu ochokera kwa mulangizi wa chitetezo wa NZC yemwe akuyanganira, kwapangidwa chiganizo kuti BLACKCAP sapitilira ndi ulendo wawo. zinayankhulidwa kuchokera ku gulu la masewero a clicket la New zealand anataero.
Akulu akuluaku Pakistan anayankha mokwiya , kunena chiganizocho, "ndichambali imodzi" komanso coononga chithunzi thunzi cha Pakistan. " Palibe aliyense wa gulu la zachitetezo athu omwe analandilapo chizindikiro chilichonse choopsea chitetezo., Nduna Sheikh Rasheed Ahmed anatero. Anaonjezera kuti ofesi yawo yaikulu ya Pakistan idadzipeleka kupangitsa masewero popanda oonelera, koma anakana ganizori. Pakistani Federal Minister forMaritime Affairs Ali Haider Zaidi adati iye adakhumudwa pachiganizochi. " Mokwiya" a global politics anawina pama sewero akulu a clicket! panalibepo chiopsezo pachitetezo! pa jacindaardem, " anatero pouza nduna yaku New zealand patamba lawo lamchezo la tweeter.
Nduna Imran Khan paiye yekha anaitana nduna Jcinda Ardern kutsimikizira za chitetezo cha magulu amasewero, koma iwo anakhalabe kuchiganizo cha gulu lawo lamasewero,kumbali ya Ahamed komanso Pakistani Cricket Board(PCB). Bungwe la PCB anati anakonza chitetezo champhamvu kwambri "kwa magulu amasewero obwera ndipo akulu akulu chitetezo aku New zealand akanakhutitsidwa ndi madongosolo. Anthu okonda masewero a cricket ku New zealand komanso pandiko lonse akhala okhumudwa ndichiganizo chobwera nthawi yotha itha kukana kusewera, "oyang'anira zamasewerowa anatero.Wamkulu oyang'anira Black Caps, David White, anati sakanatha kukana uphungu omwe amalandira. Ndikumvetsetsa kuti ichi chikhara chopweteka kwa PCB, Omwe akhara akuyendetsa, koma chitetezo kwa osewera ndichofunikira kwmbiri, ndipo tikukhulupilira kuti ichi ndiye chinali chisankho choyenera, anatero. MBli ziwirizi zimayenera kusewera masewero atattu tsiku limodzi ku Rawalpindi, yomwe imadziwika nndi dzina loti twin city mu mzinda waukulu waku Pakistani,Islamabad,motsogozana ndi masewero olumikizana a five limited over kapena t-20s mumzinda waukulu wachiwiri ku Pakistani, Lahore.
Wamkulu oyang'anira bungwe la PCB, Wasim Khan, wauza VOA kuti gulu lawo lamaswero lidzibwelera kwawo Loweluka pa ndege yawo yapadera. Gulu la masewero a cricket ya azungu inauzidwa kuti izabwere ku Pakistani mu October, Koma nduna Alhamed wti ulendo umenewonso pakali pano ndiokaikitsa.Unduna wa zamkatiwandidziwitsa ine kuti gulu lamasewero la azunguli nalonso likuganiza mofanana nawo. Kumbali yathu ife ndiokomzeka kuwalandira. palibe chiopsezo chilichonse cha chitetezo mudziko lathu ungakhale ku New zealand kapenanso ku England, " iye anatero. magulu amasewero a cricket amaiko anasiya kupita ku Pakistani chifukwa cha chiwembu chomwe chinachitikira gulu lamasewero a criket la Sri Lankan mu 2009 ku Lahore komwe kunavulala osewera agululi okwana asanu ndi awiri. Pakistani yadutsa dzaka zambiri mudzipolowe kuambira chamma 2007 pamene gulu lina la mtundu wa anthu sili magwilizana ndi pakistani pokhala mbali imodzi ndi United States mu nkhondo yawo pomwe zifwamba zinayamba limbana ndi onse achitetezo komanso anthu wamba. Akulu akulu aboma la Pakistani anati mzika zawo zoposera 80,000 zafa paziwembuzo, ndipo dziko lazunzika ndikuonongeka kwa chuma chawo choposera $150 billion. Mu 2016 akulu akulu acriket anapanga bungwe la Pakistani Super League, magulu oswera okwana asanu ndi imodzi amaimilira mizinda isanu ndi umodzi. mgagulu osewerawa amaphatikiza osewera akunja mukuyesetsa kofuna kudzutsanso masewero a criket amaiko akunja ku Pakistan. Zigawo ziwiri zamasewerowo zimaseweredwa kunja kwa Pakistanku United Arab Emirates.Gulu lamasewero loyamba kubwelera ku Pakistan linali Zimbabwe mu 2015
Atsogoleri amu Africa akambirana njira zochepetsera kuonongeka kwa kusintha kwa nyengo.
Akulu akulu amulingu wapamwamba a m'boma anakumana mowilikiza sabata ino pokambirana mavuto omwe Africa akukumana nawo pofuna kukomza kukura kwa chiwelengero cha anthu pamabali yakusintha kwa nyengo. Mkumanawu cholinga chake kunali kupeza njira zomwe maboma amu Africa angatahnirane ndimavuto amenewa pochepetsa kapena kupewa mkangano..
Africa imapanga pafupifupi 3% ya malo omwe amachotsa mpweya oipa mulengalenga, ali pansi pa makomtineti onse, koma ndizosafunikira kwambiri kusiyana ndi zigawo zonse zapa dzikolapansi, pakuti Africa imadalira kwambiri pa zachilengedwa chawo pa zakudya, madzi komanso mankhwala.
Kuyankhula pa mkumano wa pakanema Lchiwiri pa zanyengo, mikangano ndi chiwelengero cha anthu mu Africa, wachiwiri wa mtsogoliri wa dziku la Nigeria Yemi Osibanjo anati amaboma amu Africa akuyenera kumaganizira za nyengo pamene akuyesera kukweza chuma chawo.
Undindo wathu oyambilira wa ife ndi maiko amu Africa ukuyenera nthawi zonse kukhara owonetsetsa chisamaliro cha anthu anthu kudzera pakupeza zithandizo zapamwamba, kuphatikizilapo magetsi, thandizo la zaumoyo, maphunziro, ncthito zotetezeka komanso malo achitetezo kupatikiza mafuta ophikira abwino, Tikuyenera titsogoze myankho omwe ali ogwilizana ndi chitukuko komanso ali ndi cholinga cha zanyengo, ndipo ichi ndichofunikira kwambiri, anatero Osinbajo.
Bungwe la Center for Research on the Epidemiology of Disasters, lomwe lili ku Brussels, linanena izi mu 2019, Africa yapezeka ndikuvuta kwakukulu kwa nyengo ndi mulingo wa 56 kusiyana ndi 45 pa mulingo wa zaka za mmbuyo .
kuchita kwa nyengo yovutayi kwa khudza miyoyo ya anthu 16.6 miliyoni mmaiko 29. pafupifupi 13 milliyon mwa iwo anali ochokera ku maiko asanu: Kenya, Mozambique, Somalia, Tanzania ndi Zimbabwe.
chigawo chakumadzulo cha Africa chili ndi nyengo zoononga zochepa komabe vuto lakuonongeka kwa mpweya wamulengalenga kukumawakhudza chimodzi modzi.
Nduna yoona za nyengo ku Ghana Kwaku Afriyie anafotokoza momwe kusintha kwa nyengo kwa khudzira malo aulimi mdzikomo.
"Kuvuta ndikupitilira kwa kuvuta kwa nyengo yoononga ku mpoto kwa Ghana mosakaikitsa zionjezera kukula kwa kusowa chakudya ndipo zipangitsa anthu kuchoa ku mpoto kupita ku mwera. Ndipo kupatura izikuchuluka kwa madzi osefukula ndikukhalitsa kwa chilara kupangitsa anthu kusamuka. Kalembera wa anthu anaonetsa izi zaka zochepa zapitazo,pakhala kusamuka kwa mkati komwe kawchitika ku Ghana chifukwa chakuchitika kwa ngozi zadzidzi ngakhalenso kudutsa zipata zathu, Iye anatero.
Katswiri oimilira maiko amu United Nations (U.N) ku maiko amu mgwiriano wa mu Africa ( African Union) Hannah Tetteh, anati kontineti ikufunika kupititsa patsogolo njira zofalitsira nkhani kunja ndi mgwirizano okonza zokhudzana ndikuvuta kwa nyengo.
"Sikuti vuto lakhala kuti sitinamange zinthu zimenezi. Vuto lakhala kuti sitinazigwilitsebe ntchito bwino, izizi zikulozabenkhani ya umodzi mdziko komanso kusowekera kwa kufuna kwa anthu a mu dziko kukhala nawo ena monga zinalili kukhala nacho chidwi chochitachita komanso mwina kulangiza zinthu zomwe tingachite kuti tigonjetse vuto lina lake. Ndipo ngati tingazindikire tili limodzimu izi, kenako zinthuzi zikuyenera kusintha," iye anatero.
Pa maganizo apaderadera, Osinbajo anapeleka maganizo akuti boma limalimbikitsa kugwiritsa ntchito mpweya wa chilengedwe komanso kubzyala mitengo ndicholinga chosunga nkhalango zomwe zimayamwa mpweya oyipa wa carbondioxide komanso kupewetsa kuetentha kwa dziko lonse komwe kumadza ndi kuonongeka kwa bulangete ya mlengalenga.
Achinyamata aku Afrika avutika ndi ntchito, mapahunziro mkatikati mwa mlili
Tsogolo limkaoneka lowala pa Tinashe Mapuranga, ophunzira ntchito pa nkhokwe ya ndalama (bank) yotsogola ku Zimbabwe yemwe anaoneka kuti adzapeza mwayi olembedwa ntchito pompo akamaliza maphunziro ake a ukachenjede. Patatha izi mlili wa COVID 19 unakantha.
Mkatikati mwa kutseka zipata zolowera mmayiko, wachinyamata wa zaka 24 yu anali mmodzi mwa omwe anachotsedwa ndipo alibe chiyembekezo pa nthawi ya kumaliza maphunziro ake chifukwa cha kutsekatseka kwa masukulu
"Izi zandisokoneza kwambili paphunziro anga ndithu. Ndilibe ndalama zogulira mayunitsi a pa intaneti(data) komanso ndilibe laptop yangayanga kuti ndikwanitse kuphunzira nawo pa intaneti ndikupitiliza kuphunzira monga azanga akuchitira.," anatero Mapuranga, amene amakhala ndi mai ake ku Chitungwiza, dera lomwe lili ndi anthu ambili odalira maganyu kummawa kwa ku mwera kwa Harare, likulu la dzikoli.
"Ndimayenera kumaliza mu Novembara chaka cha 2021 koma pakanali pano, sitinaphunzire zambili," Iye anatero. " Kunena zoona, sindikudziwa kuti ndimaliza liti maphunziroanga a sukulu ya ukachenjede. Ndikufunitsitsa nditamaliza komanso ndikupeza ntchito , kenako ndikuchita zinthu zooneka mmoyo."
Nthawi yambili ya Mapuranga amakhala ku nyumba, kusamalira kadimba ka masamba komwe banja lakwawo limapezerapo chakudya. Mayi ake amazithandizira mmoyo wawo popita ku dziko la South AFRICA kukagulitsa ziboliboli. Ndi masache mmiseu, amodzi a malonda omwe akhudzidwa kwambili ndi mliliwu.
"Takhala tikuyesetsa kugwira ntchito molimbika kuti tipeze ndalama," iye anatero. Ndinayesera kupanga malonda aang'ono ogulitsa nkhuni mu misewu koma adindo anatithamangitsamo. Bambo anga anamwalira. Mayi anga machita malonda osakhazikika omwe nawo ayima kamba kakutseka zipata za mayiko. Zinthu sizili bwino pakali pano. zathina."
Nyengo ya Mapuranga itha kumaoneka yakakasi, koma iye wati ali nkdi nkhawa chifukwa cha amzake omwe samagwira ntchito omwe atayikira ku mowa, mankhwala ozunguza ubongo komanso uhule.
"Achinyamata ambili ataya chiyembekezo," iye natero
Mu Afrika, ambili ofanana ndi Mapurangaakuvutika mndi kuvuta kwa chuma komwe kwadza chufkwa cha COVID-19, kutha kwa ntchito komanso kuona kusokonezedwa kwa maphunziro awo, kafukufuku waanthu a zaka za pakti pa 18 ndi 24 mu mayiko 15 wapeza zimenezi.
