Zimbabwe ikutsegulira Victoria falls kwa alendo aku mayiko akunja omwe anabaitsa katemera
Zimbabwe ikutsegula malo otchuka okopa alendo a ku mayiko a kunja Kwa alendo omwe analandira katemera wa COVID 19, mu zochitika zomwe zalandilidwa ndi gawo lokopa alendo lomwe lavutika. Patatha mkumano wa nduna za boma madzuo a lachiwiri, nduna youlutsa nkhani, a Monica Mutsvangwa anauza atolankhani kuti boma laganiza kuti lichotse chotchinga pa Victoria Falls, omwe ndi dziwe lalitali pa dzikolonse lapansi lomwelimakopa alendo ambili mu dzikolo.
Ndunazi zamva pempho la gawo la zokopa alendo kuti atsegure Victoria falls komanso chipata cha mmalire cha Kazungula kwa alendo omwe analandira katemera mokwanira. Chiganizochi chabwera poona kuti anthu oposera 60 pa anthu 100 aliwonse okhala ku Victoria falls analandira katemera. Komabe njira zopewera mliliwu zomwe zinabwera ndi kutseka kwa zipata zikupitilira kutsatilidwa dziko lonse pofuna kupewa kukula kwa mliliwu maka mumtundu wachitatu wake," anatero Mtsvangwa. Godfrey Koti, oyankhulira Zimbabwe Tourism Authority wati mliliwu unagwetsa gawo la zokopa alendo pa dziko lonse . Anatindi nthawi yoti Zimbabwe iyambe kuzitolera kubwerera patali pomwe inagwa pa kutsegulidwa kwa Victoria falls, mkatikati mwa kutsata njira zopewera mlili wa COVID 19. "Poyang'anira mbali ya chigawo, kuenda kwa aendo kukula ndipo izi zipeleka uthenga komanso chithuzithuzi cha mphamvu kwa otitsatira malonda athu.Iyi ndi njira yoonetsa, yopindulitsa konetsedwa kuchokera kufunitsitsa kwa boma kuti abaye katemera anthu onse a ku Voictoriafalls potsatira izi Victoria falls kulimba ku mliliwu.Choncho ndife okondwera kwambili poona izi zikuchitika ndipo zikoonetsa kuti tikupita njira yoyenera," antero Koti. Pafupifupi anthu1.5 ochokeramu chiwerengero cha Zimbabwe cha 14 million alandira katemera wawo woyamba, ndipo pafupifupi 695,000 alandira wachiwiri
Clement Mukwasi, oankhulira a Shearwater,amodzimwa oyendetsa Victoria Falls, anamveka ndi chiyembekezo chabwino. "Ndi chiyembekezo cha gawo la zoona alendoli kuti mapeto a mliliwu-omwe tikuganiza kuti tafikamo- kudzakhala mpata wopatsidwa ngongole zopelekedwa ku gawoli kuti libwerere. Tikuyamikira boma pokumva pempho lathu kuti atsigure zipata zolowera mdziko muno za dziko la Zambia ndi Botswanachifukwa Victoria falls ndiyotetezekakwa thunthu. Tikuyembekeza kuti pamwamba pa kutsegura zipata ayikanso mfundo kapena lamulo la momwe anthu aziyendera polowa mmayiko atatu onsewa.,"anatero. Mukwasi anati iwo amene anabayidwa aloledwe kuyenda polowa ndikutuluka mdzikoli opanda mavuto pamene iwo amenen sanabayitse aziyamba aonetsa zotsatira zoikira umboni kuti alibe kapena sanapezeke ndi kachilombo ka corona kamene kamayambitsanthenda ya COVID-19. Zimbabwe ili ndi anthu okwana 101,711 omwe anapezeka ndi matenda oyambitsidwa ndi kachilombo ka Corona komanso anthu 3,280 omwe anamwalira ndi mliliwu potengera zotsatira zomwe zinapezedwa ndi a Hopkins University omwe akuutsata mlili wa dziko lonsewu. Boma lati ndondomeko yobayitsa katemera ikura mankhwala ena akangofika kuchokera ku dziko la China mu masiku ali mkudzawo. Chiwelengero cha nathu opezeka ndi mliliwu chikuchulukira pamene tundu wa delta ukufalikira kwambili.
UNHCR Voices yokhudzidwa dziko la Botswana litabweza anthu othawa kwawo a ku Zimbabwe
Ofesi ya U.N. High Commissioner for Refugees (UNHCR) ndiyokhudzika pamene dziko la botswana linathamangitsa anthu othawa kwawo aku zimbabwe omwe akhala m'dziko lawo kuyambira 2008. Anthu othawa kwawowa analephera kulembetsa mwakufuna kwawo kuti abwerere kwawo, zomwe zinapangitsa kuchotsedwa kwawo mokakamizakumapeto kwa sabata yathayi. wa pampando oyang'anira ma ubale akunja wa UNHCR (external relations officer) Kate Pond wati anthu othawa kwawowa kupatura momwe iwo analili, ali ndi ufulu wachibadidwe ndipo akanaloledwa kukhala ku dzikolo kwa muyaya. "UNHCR ndiyokhudzikabe kuti anthu a kuZimbabwe omwe anakhala ku Botswana kwa zaka zopitilira khumi(10) achotsedwa kubwerera ku Zimbabwe osati mwa kufuna kwawo.Kupatura kuti anthuwa anali motani, anthuwa akanali ndi ma ufulu enabe ndipo UNHCR inakakonda njira zina zokonzera zinthu monga momwe zimakhalira ndi anthu ena a ku Zimbabwe omwe ali ndi abale ku Botswana kuti athe kukhazikikabe mdzikomo, "anatero Pond. Mmodzi mwa anthu othamangitsidwawa, yemwe anayankhura ndipo anakana kudziulura, anati anamasulidwa lachinayi ndipo anauzidwa kuti akakwere basi yomwe iwatengele iwo kuchipata cha Zimbabwe. " Tinachoka ku Botswana ndi njala.Tinatumizidwa ku chipata ndipo sitinapeze thandizo lina lililonse. Timkafuna kukhalabe ku Botswana; ndichifukwa sitinalembetse( kuti tibwelele kwathu.). Tilibe kalikonse, sitikudziwa pokayambira, tinali ndi ana omwe amapita ku sukulu. Zikakhala zovutachifukwa chosakhala ndi zitupa ngati chitupa coyendera mmaiko komanso zitupa zazizindikiro(ID), " anatero mmodzi mwa othawa kwawoyu.Othamangitsidwawa akhala akukhara kumalo osungirako anthu othawa kwawo kotchedwa Dukwi refugee camp.Boma la Botswana linachenjeza iwo othawa maiko akwawo kuti ngati salembetsa adzathamangitsidwa. Mwezi watha Dziko La Botswana linatumiza kwawo anthu ena oposera 200 adziko la Zimbabwe omwe analembetsa mwakufuna kwawo zakubwelera kudziko lakwawo. Anthu othawa dziko lakwawo ofuna kubwelerawa koyamba anakana, akuti chifukwa cha mantha akuzunzidwa mudziko lakwawo. Ambiri anali otsutsa boma amene nyumba zawo zinaotchedwa munthawi yoopsa ya misonkhano yokopa anthu paudindo wa mtsogoleri wa dziko mu chaka cha 2008. Koma mmodzi mwa obwelera, Bheki Weza, anati anadabwa atalandilidwa bwino mu dziko la Zimbabwe mosiyana ndi nkhawa zomwe analinazo za chitetezo koyambilira. "Ndife okondwa kwambiri ndimmene zinthu zilili. Pomwe ndikunena pano, Ndili kunyumba stopano kuyesa kukhazikika komanso kudzikonzekeretsa kunyengo zovuta za chuma zomwe zili kuno ku Zimbabwe. Komabe ndine okondwa chifukwa pali mtendere pakati pathu. Ndakumana ndi mafumu komanso ndakumana ngakhale ndi anthu ena omwe timkamenyana nawo tisanachoke. Pakadali pano zilibwino, anatero Weza. Bungwe la UNHRC lati lipitiliza kuthandiza anthu othawa maiko akwawo omwe anabwelera kwawo. Munthu aliyense walandira $520 komanso phukusi la chakudya. koma othandizawa ati sipadzikhara thandizo loeteri kwa anthu othawa kwawo omwe athamangitsidwawa.
