Zuma wa ku South Africa aimba mlandu oimirira boma
Mtsogoleri wopuma wa dziko la South Africa akufuna kuzenga mlandu ochotsa oimilira boma wamkulu pa kuyankha mlandu wa mgwilizano wa katangale wogula zida za nkhondo atalephera zopinga zamalamuro zomwe zinawalaka, bungwe lake linanena choncho la mulungu.
Mwezi watha bwalo lalikulu la milandu la Supreme Court of Appeal (SCA) linaononga cholinga cha Zuma chomwe amafuna kuchotsa otsogolera mlandu wa boma dzina lake Bill Downer pomuneneza kuti anali okondera komanso anatulutsa nkhani ya chinsinsi kumpatsa mtolankhani zomwe zili zotsutsana ndi lamulo la dziko kukhudzana ndi oimba mlandu, pamwamba pa zodandaura zina.
SCA inakana pempho lochotsalo kuti apemphe pa chifukwa chakuti palibe chiyembekezo chanzeru chakumbana komanso palibe chifukwa champhamvu chopaangitsa dandaulolo limveredwe
Oyankhula mmalo mwa Jacob Zuma Foundation, Mzwanele Manyi ananena pa mkumano woulutsa nkhani kuti langizo la Zuma kwa omuimilira mlandu ake kuti aimbe mlandu " tsopano lichitika mu masiku ochepa akudzawa,"
Iye ananenanso kuti gulu loimilira mlandu Zuma lalembera kuganiziraponso pa dandaulo kwa mtsogoleri waSCA, dandaulo Lkuti atchere khutu ku pempho lawo.
Zuma amene anatulutsidwa ku chipani cholamulira boma cha African Congress mu 2018 patatha zaka pafupifupi makumi awiri(20) ali mtsogoleri wapezeka wosalakwa pa milandu ya katangale, kupanga ndalama zambili mosayenera komanso kupanga malonda osayenera komanso achinyengo mu mlandu womwe wakhala ukayenda kwa kanthawipanjhani ya kugura zida za nkhodndo mwa chinyengo mu zaka za m'ma 1990.
Mlanduwu unamkakamira Zuma pakuti anachotsedwa ngati wachiwiri kwa mtsogoleri wa dzikomu chaka cha 2005. Iye anati anakhudzidwa chifukwa chakulondana mu ndale
Lolemba, mlandu womwe watenga nthawi kuti anthu aonekere ku bwalo la milandu wakonzeka kuti uyambikendipo Zuma akapezeka ku bwalo lamilanduko
Mani anati Zuma amaene akukwanitsa zaka 80 zakubadwa lachiwilili, akulemba pempho losintha masiku kupita patsogolo chifukwa " zikuchita kuonekeratu kuti zinthu zopangitsa kumva mlandu mwachilungamo palibepo"
Lolemba gulu lake ayankha kalata yolembedwa ndi malumbiro yomwe inalembedwa ndi bungwe la National Prosecution Authority pamene akufuna kupeza umboni watsopano pa kuyesedwa mu mlanduwu
"Chimene olemekezeka mtsogoleri Zuma akufunitsitsa ndilakukhala ndi tsiku lake ku bwalo lamilandu, kuyesedwa mwachilungamo komansomumkumano omwe sukutulutsidwa mosaloledwa ndi boma" Mani antero
South Africa ilibe mbali pa nkhani yomwe Russia akuika pa chiopsezo ma ubale apa dziko lonse la pansi: ozukuta
goleri wa dziko la South Africa a Cyril Ramaphosa lolemba anaonetsa kusatenga mbali kwake pamene Russia yalowa ndi aslikali, kuitanitsa kuyankhurana osati kutsutsa
Odzudzula anena motsutsana ndi boma polephera kuthamndizira dziko la Ukraine motsutsana ndi dziko loyandikana nalo. Ozukuta nkhani ati dziko la South Africa likulora mbili ya maubale ndale ndichuma mogwirizna ndi dziko la Moscow kuika pa chiopsezo ma ubalendi dziko lonse la pansi.
Njira imene Ramaphosa akufuna itachitika pokonza kusamvana kwa pakati pa Russia ndi Ukraine ndi kukambilana osati kugwilitsa ntchito zida kapena kusokonezana pa chuma
Ganizo losatekeseka lomwe Ramaphosa watenga lakana pempho lomwe gawo loyang'anira za maubale ndi maiko a kunja la dzikolo la International realtions department kuti Russia ichotse agulu la nkhondo lake.
Leaza Jernberg amakhala ku Johannesburg ndipo amapanga kafukufuku moziimira paekha okhudzana ndi ma ubale a kunja kwa dziko.
"Gawo laInternational Relations and Cooperation lomwe limaona ma ubala a mayiko a kunja kwa South Africa, zomwe anaganiza poyambilira zinali kuti 'iziz ndizosayenera. Ndipo is mu njira ina zinabwezedwa ndi mawu a mtsogoleri wa dzikolo amene ndikuganiza ali ndi ganizo la mgwilizano ndi Russia ndi momwe izi zikuonekera," Jernberg anatero. "Choncho mkati mwa South Africa momwe, mbali ya dzikoli ndilotsutsidwa, ngakhale mu boma momwemo."
Ubale wa South Africa ndi Russia ikuchokera mu zaka za ma 1960 pamene mgwirizano wa Soviet Union unapeleka thandizo kwa anthu amene amamenyera ufulu kutsutsana ndi kusalana chifukwa cha mtundu
Mu zaka zotsatira, a ndale kuphatikizipa a chipani cholamulira cha the African National Congress, anakhalabe mu ubale ndi Russia.
Ichi ndi chifukwa chake akatswiri ozukuta nkhani anati sizodabwitsa kuti maziko mwe anaikidwa ndi mtsogoleri wa kale Jacob Zuma ayankhula mogwirizana ndi mtsogoleri wa Russia Vladimir Putin
