Interpol yapeleka uthenga pa dziko lonse kuti anyamata a banja la a Gupta akufunika ku South Africa
Dziko la South Africa lati bungwe la apolisi oyang'ana zifwamba la International Criminal Police Organisation , Interpol yapempha mayyiko asake komanso kumanga Rajeshndi Atul omwe ndi abanja limodzi komanso onse a mapanga ma bizinesi omwe akuganizilidwa kuti anapeleka ziphuphu akuluakulu a aboma kuphatikizapo mtsogoleri wa dziko wopuma a Jacob Zuma kuti apeze mgwirizano wa malonda a phindu lalikulu ndi boma.
Anthu omenyerera kutha kwa zinyengo ku South Africa anena a kwa Gupta wa kuti 'analinjata boma' mawu ogwilitsidwa ogwiritsidwa ntchito pofuna kutanthauza kuti anyamatawa anali ndi mphamvu yaikulu pa tsogoleri wa dziko opuma a Jacob Zuma komanso nduna zake - machitachita omwe anasefukira ku migwirizano ya malonda, lamulo komanso zisankho za umunthu pa yekha
kugula makuba zazing'ono zokwana $1.5 million
Bungwe loyimba anthu ,ilandu mu dziko la South africa la National Prosecuting Authority linapempha ma uthenga a dziko lonsewa chaka chatha koma oimilira milandu wa Rajesh ndi Atu Gupta anatsutsa. Kupemphaku kumayenera kuunikidwa ndi Interpol kuti ionetsetse pa mwamba pa zinthu zinthu zina kuti panalibe kukondera (chifukwa cha ndale) kwina kuli konse.
Kazembe wa Interpol kwa 'the Turn Back Crime Campaign' Andy Mashaile anatidziko la South Africa linatenga nthawi kuti lisunge mgwirizano ndi dziko la united Arab Emirates pakuti azichimwenewa ali ku Dubai.
" mutha tsono kupita ku Interpol a ku Dubai ndikukanena kuti: 'Interpol Dubai, tikudziwa kuno ndi kumene anayamatawa akukhala ndipo nsewu wake dzina lake ndi ili komanso numbala ya nsewuwo ndi iyi, umu ndi momwe amaonekera, izi ndizo zithunzi zawo. Chonde tithandizeni tiwatenge anthu awa kosungirako anthu kapena ku ma selo anu, mu ndende mpaka titawatenga kuchokera ku Dubai," Mashaile anatero
Interpol ili ndi mayiko 194 omwe imagwirako ntchito ndipo pamene uthenga wa dziko lonse sumawakakamiza kumanga anthu, ma uthengawa amathandiza namlondora odziwa komwe anthu oganizilidwawo or othawawo. Zithunzi zawo zimaikidwa mu ndondomeko yothandizira kusunga lamulo.
Katswiri wa za ndale Sanusha Naidu waku Global Dialogue anati ma uthenga a dziko lonse akanathandizira kukopa anthu pa kuponyanso voti kusankha mtsogoleri wa dziko la mu chaka cha 2024 , CyrilRamaphosa chifukwa zikuonetsa kuti akuchitapo kanthu potsutsana ndi katangale
" Koma ndikuganiza kuti zomwe izi zikuonetsera ndi zakuti pa dziko lonse lapansi, mukudziwa inu, kupangitsa bungwe la dziko lonse la pansi makamaka la Interpol kuti litengepo gawo ndikulumikizana ndi ganizo lomwe Ramaphosa ali nalo," Naidu anatero. "Choncho ndikuganiza kuti iye popita patsogolo komanso poyesera kuwauza anthu a ku South Africa kuti ndikuchita zomwe ndikuenera kuchita. Ndikuzikoza izi, ndikulondoloza pa izi."
Komabe, Naidu anati alibe kutsinmikiza mtima kuti n'zokwanira kupulumutsa chipani cha African National Congress, chomwe chakhala pang'ono ndi pang'ono chikutaya awatsatira ku zisankhochifukwa cha ziphuphu zosatha komanso kulephera kukwanilitsa zinthu zofunikira
"Ndikuganiza kuti ukafuna kukamba zofuna za mzika ya wamba ya dziko la South Africa,akufuna za malamulo ndi chilungamo chiyende momwe hcimayenerera," anatero iye. "Koma funso linanso ndi la kuti kodi ndalama zonse zobebdwa mudzikoli zimabwerera bwanji? Chifukwa mukaziganizira, pamenepo ndipamene pali povuta."
Nkahni yokhudza uthenga opita dziko lonse la pansi inafika tsiku lomwe mawa lake kunatuluka uthenga wina pa kufufuza kwa kugwidwa kwa dziko. Izi zinaitanira pa National Prosecution Authority kuti amufufuze Zuma. Mtsogoleri wa kaleyu anakana kuonekera pakufufuzidwaku ndipo anakhala mu ndende kwa miyezi 15 atanyozera langizo labwalo la milandu. Komabe, anatulutsidwa kamba ka matenda zitangotha izi.
