Mzibambo wa dziko la South Africa walandira chirango pa mulandu wootcha pomwe naotcha gawo lalikulu la nyumba yamalamulo yakale.
Zandile Christimas Mafe wa zaka 39 anakaonekera lachiwiri ku bwalo lamilandu. Akulandira zilango zochuluka zokhudzana ndi moto, kuphatikiza uchigawenga, kuotcha, kuphwanya ndikulowa komanso kuba.
Mefa anamangidwa moto utangoyamba kuyaka kumene pa nyumba yamalamulo mu Cape Town mmaora oyambilira apa 2 january.
Iye mokakikilidwa anapezeka ndi malaputopu, zitupa ndi ziwiya zaku khitchini pakatundu yemwe anali naye, woimba mulandu waboma pano akuti analinso ndi zipangizo zophulika, zomwe zikuonjezera chilango cha uchigawenga
Mukuonekera kwake ku bwalo lamilandu omuimilira pamulanduwu anakana milandu yonseyi pa ozengedwayu.
Mafe wakhala akusintha omuimilira pamulandu, ndipo pakadali pano akuimililidwa ndi Dali Mpofu omwe ndiotchuka, yemwe wakhara akuthandizana ndi achipani cha ndale cha Left-wing EconomicFreedom Fighters.
Mpofe wakharanso akuimilira mtsogoleli opuma wadziko Jacob Zuma, yemwe anamangidwa posalemekeza malamulo a bwalo lamilandu.
Kumva madandaulo oti Mafe aziyendera mulandu kuchokera kwawo kwasunthidwa mpakapa 11 February ndipo amangidwira ku bungwe losunga amisara.
Zaululika kuti anayambapo watumizidwanso kukayesedwa misara pa 3 January ndipo anapezeka ndimatenda amisara amu ubongo a paranoid Schizophrenia.
Mulingo oyesezera kuonongeka kwa malo anyumba yamalamulo ndioposa 14 miliyoni pa ndalama ya U.S dollars. Pamenepo osaphatikizira ndalama za katundu osunthika wamkati, ngati makompyuta ndi mipando.
